{"tid":1679395,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港警隊「守護咭」計劃","createTime":"2019-10-28T07:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T07:44:10.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc960ece61badc2f13454c6497839aec7517b931","tid":1679395,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"打人同埋侮辱人之前..<br />\n香港警隊十分重視保障精神上無行為能力人士(MIP)的權利，並會確保需要警方協助的MIP<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">受到尊重及獲得公平對待</span></span>，而他們的特殊需要亦應得到適切的照顧。<br />\n<br />\n為優化對MIP社群的服務，香港警隊推出一系列的新措施，包括「守護咭計劃」、「行為指標」及「合適成人通知書」，冀更能照顧MIP的需要及促進彼此了解。在推出新措施的同時，警隊為所有常規警員、輔警及文職人員舉辦針對MIP需要旳專題培訓，加強他們接觸MIP時的專業敏感度。<br />\n<br />\n打人侮辱人哋之後....<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1146/images/20191022_4f0aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1146%2Fimages%2F20191022_4f0aa.jpg&h=5796c702&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2180d22d2084c1b5456c02da636e5a8140baa088","tid":1679395,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3gbRGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3gbRGC.jpg&h=94dd7b77&s={SIZE}\" />老豆搵仔：新疆單野俾譚仔搞到沉晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676450</a></blockquote>"}]}